name: Burnmaster
0:
”Alexa, open Burn master”
”Alexa, start Burn master”
”Alexa, ask Burn master for a burn”
skdetail:
Rated: Mature. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: burn master
des:
Try the Burnmaster to add more fun to your day. Want to burn friends, have them activate the Burnmaster. Want to burn yourself, you know what to do, activate Burn master. When using the skill, you can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next burn. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill.
